title: Awaken Your Mind DVD
description:
I created this DVD for people interested in awakening their consciousness to the new reality unfolding.  This is a compilation of various videos collected and created by me for you.

If you are interested in:

Paranormal
UFOs
Crop Circles
Energy Healing
Free Energy

this is for you.


If not, at the very least, this will entertain you...
At best, it will assist you in raising your conscious awareness of the miraculous events occurring around the world and above and hopefully move you into action to awaken others around you so that we can change this reality from a nightmare to a blissful paradise.  The choice is ultimately ours.

This video is not to be taken as Gospel or on Faith alone.  I encourage you to investigate these topics to your necessary level for raising your awareness.

As always, take away what has value for you in the moment and leave what is left for later.

I wish you and ALL Beings PEACE, JOY, and LOVE!

~ Will
